		<title type="html"><![CDATA[Women&#039;s writing:  dead or alive]]></title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://languagelog.ldc.upenn.edu/nll/?p=48618&#038;utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=womens-writing-dead-or-alive" />

