<li>"<a title="Permanent link to Hong Kong-specific characters and shorthand" href="http://languagelog.ldc.upenn.edu/nll/?p=18175" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://languagelog.ldc.upenn.edu/nll/?p%3D18175&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1601745934017000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGNN3KUH89E6z1Se_JVr-AE-kv60A">Hong Kong-specific characters and shorthand</a>" (3/15/15), with links to relevant websites for restaurant shorthand characters</li>
<li>"<a title="Permanent link to General Tso's chikin" href="http://languagelog.ldc.upenn.edu/nll/?p=4682" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://languagelog.ldc.upenn.edu/nll/?p%3D4682&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1601745934017000&amp;usg=AFQjCNFUHHDX9j7TQS1gDKpbBNt-QfyAcA">General Tso's chikin</a>" (6/11/13), especially in the comments</li>
<li>"<a title="Permanent link to Writing: from complex symbols to abstract squiggles" href="https://languagelog.ldc.upenn.edu/nll/?p=43172" target="_blank" rel="bookmark noopener noreferrer" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://languagelog.ldc.upenn.edu/nll/?p%3D43172&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1601745934017000&amp;usg=AFQjCNFSibzCcJLek5a8gwpI5NGj1jKVtg">Writing: from complex symbols to abstract squiggles</a>" (6/11/19)</li>
</ul>
<p>[h.t. Chau Wu]</p>
]]></content>
		
